data.database_description: This database appears to manage music-related data, including artists, albums, tracks, and genres. It also handles customer information, employee details, invoices for purchases, and playlists. The schema is structured with clear relationships between tables through foreign keys, facilitating complex queries on sales data, artist performances, and customer preferences.
